ʔēyfo ʔādam
gam ʔādam ba Nēgev ze naḳōn
loʔ gavōah gavōah Hagāri ʔal taṣīmi ʔet ha daysā ʕal ha roʔš ki ʔaz nicṭarēḳ
ʔavāl ʔim ʔat taʕaṣī ʔet ze gavōah gav
loʔ ʔanī loʔ ʔohēvet daysā todā

